{"id": 2536, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都用过哪些“快餐式”追剧方式？", "description": "欢迎进入“两倍速追剧”时代。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 12406, "comment_count": 39, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180925175138jcm0eWYDf2wS6kUh.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-09-25T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4747, "title": "你都用过哪些“快餐式”追剧方式？", "content": "你都用过哪些“快餐式”追剧方式？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 300327, "content": "两倍速看，一直快进，只在关键时刻停下来", "image": "img/option/option/201809251747343KUvs2FOwaPkWcHL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 300328, "content": "正片看个大概，喜欢的 CP 片段刷了一遍又一遍", "image": "img/option/option/20180925175808n60gGD4rSsQ5CIdR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 300329, "content": "不看正片，通过各种截图、剧评、图解“云追剧”", "image": "img/option/option/201809251755300U71mSEv5hkWilxF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 300330, "content": "热播的时候不看，攒到播完了再一次性追掉", "image": "img/option/option/20180925175441Z7DdupyFs56lmb34.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 300332, "content": "根据场景挑剧看，比如吃饭的时候专挑“泡面番”“下饭剧”", "image": "img/option/option/20180925175321udXH4i8DocbEWxsj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 300333, "content": "只看开头和大结局，中间全靠分集剧情简介", "image": "img/option/option/20180925175431io1zY6BgWZ5TCbmF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 300334, "content": "按图索骥，只看主线or高能部分", "image": "img/option/option/20180925175418D2c3Wd6XFSNGrzfn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 300336, "content": "特别熟的老剧，当作工作/干家务时的背景音乐", "image": "img/option/option/20180925175303yClwm4Xa8AWt5qu9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}